  "texts": [
    "If The trackers are measured by using both success rate (SR) and visual object tracking (VOT) protocols.",
    "The VOT protocol evaluates the tracking performance in terms of accuracy and failure.",
    "Accuracy (Acc.)",
    "considers the IoU between ground truth and bounding box, and failure (Fail.)",
    "keeps track of zero overlap, whereby the tracker is re-initialized when there is no overlap using the ground truth, and tracking is continued."
  ],
